name: As a Amazon User I could select item and get that item into cart -- @1.1

steps.name: Given I have go to https://www.amazon.com with page title Amazon.com. Spend less. Smile more.
When I typed Apple iPhone 14 Pro in search box related to path //input[@id="twotabsearchtextbox"] and moved to page with title Amazon.com : apple iphone 14 pro

And I clicked on 1st result //div[@class="a-section aok-relative s-image-fixed-height"]//img[@data-image-index="1"] in search results and moved to page with title Amazon.com: Apple iPhone 14 Pro, 256GB, Space Black - Unlocked (Renewed) : Cell Phones & Accessories
And I clicked on add to cart button //input[@id="add-to-cart-button"] in 1st result page and moved to page with title Amazon.com Shopping Cart
Then I clicked on cart button //a[@data-csa-c-content-id="sw-gtc_CONTENT"] and get the cart page and moved to page with title Amazon.com Shopping Cart

parameters.name: page_title_1st_results
parameters.value: Amazon.com: Apple iPhone 14 Pro, 256GB, Space Black - Unlocked (Renewed) : Cell Phones & Accessories
